05  <span class="nowrap">[<a class="int-reflink" href="/pmc/articles/PMC1782186/">PMC free article</a>]</span> [<a href="/pubmed/16011518" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=pubmed&amp;article-id=2441536&amp;issue-id=201641&amp;journal-id=365&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Entrez%7CPubMed%7CRecord">PubMed</a>]</span></div><div class="ref-cit-blk half_rhythm" id="CR16">16. <span class="citation"></span><span class="citation">Dong Y, Zeng CQ, Ball JM, Estes MK, Morris AP (1997) The rotavirus enterotoxin NSP4 mobilizes intracellular calcium in human intestinal cells by stimulating phospholipase C-mediated inositol 1, 4, 5-trisphosphate production. Proc Natl Acad Sci USA 94:3960&#x02013;3965  <span class="nowrap">[<a class="int-reflink" href="/pmc/articles/PMC20550/">PMC free article</a>]</span> [<a href="/pubmed/9108087" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=pubmed&amp;article-id=2441536&amp;issue-id=201641&amp;journal-id=365&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Entrez%7CPubMed%7CRecord">PubMed</a>]</span></div><div class="ref-cit-blk half_rhythm" id="CR17">17. <span class="citation"></span><span class="citation">Estes MK (2001) Rotaviruses and their replication. In: Fields BN, Knipe DM, Howley PM (eds) Fields virology, vol 2. Lippincott/The Williams &#x00026; Wilkins Co., Philadelphia, pp 1747&#x02013;1786 </span></div><div class="ref-cit-blk half_rhythm" id="CR18">18. <span class="citation"></span><span class="citation">Geenen PL, Dopfer D, van der Meulen J, De Jong MC (2005) Transmission of F4&#x000a0;+&#x000a0;E coli in groups of early weaned piglets. Epidemiol Infect 133:459&#x02013;468  <span class="nowrap">[<a class="int-reflink" href="/pmc/articles/PMC2870269/">PMC free article</a>]</span> [<a href="/pubmed/15962552" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=pubmed&amp;article-id=2441536&amp;issue-id=201641&amp;journal-id=365&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Entrez%7CPubMed%7CRecord">PubMed</a>]</span></div><div class="ref-cit-blk half_rhythm" id="CR19">19. <span class="ci